column1: Human UBA3 could be precipitated with glutathione S - transferase ( GST) - NEDD8, but not with GST - ubiquitin or GST - sentrin - 1.

A deletion allele of ENR2 is lethal with temperature - sensitive alleles of cdc34 and enhances the phenotypes of cdc4, cdc53, and skp1, strongly implying that Rub1p conjugation to Cdc53p is required for optimal assembly or function of the E3 complex SCFCdc4.
